        <h1>🚀 ReactorPro 2025 🚀</h1>
        <h2>An Innovation and Product Design Challenge</h2>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> 13th March 2025 (10 AM - 4 PM)</p>
        <p><strong>Venue:</strong> 7th Block - Biochemical Engineering Lab</p>
        
        <h2>Event Description</h2>
        <p>ReactorPro 2025 is an exciting and innovative competition for students in Bioengineering, Chemical Engineering, Pharmaceutical Sciences, and related fields. Participants will design and present small-scale working reactor prototypes addressing real-world applications.</p>
        
        <h2>Participation Mode</h2>
        <p>👥 Team (4 members per team) - Open to students from all colleges. Interdisciplinary teams encouraged!</p>
        
        <h2>Prizes & Rewards</h2>
        <p>🏆 1st Prize: ₹7,000 | 🥈 2nd Prize: ₹5,000 | 🥉 3rd Prize: ₹3,000</p>
        
        <h2>Event Guidelines</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>✔ Open to UG & PG students in relevant fields.</li>
            <li>✔ Prototype must address Bioengineering, Chemical Engg, Pharmaceuticals, or Wastewater Treatment.</li>
            <li>✔ Max size: 2x2x2 feet.</li>
            <li>✔ Secure wiring, insulation & hazard control.</li>
            <li>✔ Functional prototype must demonstrate a working process.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Presentation & Demonstration</h2>
        <p>⏳ 10-min presentation + 5-min Q&A | 📊 Use charts, videos & visuals</p>
        
        <h2>Judging Criteria</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>✔ Innovation & Creativity (30%)</li>
            <li>✔ Functionality (25%)</li>
            <li>✔ Relevance (20%)</li>
            <li>✔ Sustainability (15%)</li>
            <li>✔ Teamwork & Presentation (10%)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Event Coordinators</h2>
