        <h2>Objectives of the Event</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>🌱 Sustainability: Energy-efficient and eco-friendly reactor designs.</li>
            <li>📈 Scalability: Small-scale prototypes with industrial applications.</li>
            <li>🤝 Interdisciplinary Collaboration: Integration of concepts from various fields.</li>
            <li>💡 Problem-Solving: Addressing industrial and environmental challenges.</li>
        </ul>
        
